@node "Main" "SnowPlants.guide/Main"
@{u}SnowPlants v1.8@{uu}

SnowPlants is another one of those fine modules for the famous
Garshneblanker screensaver.

This module constructs pictures which often look like ferns.
They consist of thousands of points falling one after another
from the top of the screen to its bottom.
Every time they hit the bottom or another - already fallen -
dot they stick to it, and the next dot begins its journey down.

You can control the speed, the colour and the size of the pictures
with the module's preferences menu.


